Empathy Map for College Students

SAYS:
"I eat whatever is available in mess"
"I don't have time to cook"
"I want to lose weight but..."

THINKS:
"I want to be healthy"
"What should I eat to gain energy?"
"Is junk food really that bad?"

DOES:
Skips breakfast
Orders food late night
Eats junk food during exams

FEELS:
Tired and lazy
Confused about diet
Stressed about health and weight

PAIN POINTS:
No nutrition information
No personalized diet plan
No time to research healthy food

GAINS:
Wants easy food suggestions
Wants to track calories
Wants to stay healthy with less effort
